sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Test Suite
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant TrainOp as Training Operator<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant Kueue as Kueue Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant Master as Training Pod (Master)<br/>Training Runtime Image
    participant Worker as Training Pod (Worker)<br/>Training Runtime Image
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Distributed Training Job (PyTorchJob)

    User->>K8sAPI: POST PyTorchJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Kueue: Workload created
    Kueue->>K8sAPI: Admit job<br/>(quota available)
    K8sAPI->>TrainOp: PyTorchJob admitted
    TrainOp->>K8sAPI: Create Master + Worker Pods
    K8sAPI-->>Master: Pod scheduled
    K8sAPI-->>Worker: Pod scheduled
    Master->>Worker: DDP init_process_group<br/>29500/TCP gRPC plaintext
    Master->>Worker: NCCL AllReduce<br/>GPU-GPU RDMA
    Worker->>S3: Download dataset<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+ AWS IAM
    S3-->>Worker: Training data
    Master->>S3: Upload model checkpoint<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+ AWS IAM
    S3-->>Master: Confirmation

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Ray Cluster Job Execution

    participant RayHead as Ray Head Node<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant RayWorker as Ray Worker Node

    User->>K8sAPI: POST RayCluster + RayJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>RayHead: Head pod created
    K8sAPI-->>RayWorker: Worker pods created
    User->>RayHead: POST /api/jobs/<br/>8265/TCP HTTP plaintext
    RayHead->>RayWorker: Task distribution<br/>6379/TCP GCS plaintext
    RayHead->>RayWorker: Ray Client<br/>10001/TCP plaintext
    RayWorker->>S3: Download data/models<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+ AWS IAM
    S3-->>RayWorker: Data artifacts
    RayHead-->>User: Job status + logs<br/>GET /api/jobs/{id}

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Kueue Job Queuing

    User->>K8sAPI: POST PyTorchJob/TrainJob<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Kueue: Workload object created
    Kueue->>K8sAPI: Check ClusterQueue capacity
    Kueue->>K8sAPI: Admit or suspend job<br/>ServiceAccount Token
